default 
defaultIn so far as any information appeared to be available, it came 
defaultfrom mobile telephone conversations passengers were making with people outside the airport.
default&#xa0;
defaultiv)
default&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
defaultThe hallmark of a competent, quality-driven enterprise is how well it can cope with the unexpected, not how we
defaultll it can manage a steady state.
default&#xa0;
